Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好暖和呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能睡啊 我們是大山少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 哪怕只剩你一個也要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達山頂之後女性魅力升級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一個人變得受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好的一起登上回憶中的大山的約定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 空調開著沒關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫雪村葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高中一年級學生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都喜歡室內活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近也開始對大山產生了興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在冬天的富士山上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 竟然把別人扔下跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向真是太冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你拿你自己做的夢來跟我抱怨我也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你平時的所作所為跑到夢裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過回憶中的大山嗎 真是讓人懷念呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 快點把帳篷搭起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這姑娘是日向 算是我的青梅竹馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀請我登山的就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.97,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,492)}住帳篷！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼小的帳篷要睡四個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疊起來看著就會很小了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展開的話很大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 搭起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我們兩個人能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來按著 你把支架從布套裏穿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把支架從布套裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個就是布套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裏把成為帳篷骨架的支架穿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 然後再穿一根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把支架的頂端插到金屬孔裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把勁兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大的帳篷 意外還挺簡單的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說我們為什麼會在日向家的院子裏搭帳篷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去山上露營？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也叫上心夏和楓 大家一起住帳篷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意 很有趣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 飯還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次 我和朋友一起去露營
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露營
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 用鋁飯盒燒飯 住帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起露營 只有女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那麼去日向家裏留宿可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 日向的爸爸也在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要給人家添麻煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 就變成在日向家的院子裏露營了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 把楔子打進去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哈巴狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ペグ（帐篷短桩）和パグ（哈巴狗）只差一个单词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楔子是指短樁啊 就在那裏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就直接說短樁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微向外側傾斜 牢牢地打進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用短樁把線繩拴起來 把全部都固定好就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 搭好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真寬敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸手伸腳都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 楓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們倆是我們的登山同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我們高一級的楓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓也是登山的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個是中學生心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個擁有很高的女性魅力 治癒系的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯的材料 我買來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 你做過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是做過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把米洗完以後蓋上蓋子 吸一會水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天用的是烤肉爐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能「開始火小中間火大的哦」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的人說明煮飯方法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}意思是煮飯剛開始的火小 中間的火大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就算小孩子哭也不要把蓋子拿下來」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}意思是蒸飯的時候不要取下蓋子 要好好蒸熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是蓋子浮起來 就壓上重物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就不會溢出來 等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往鍋裏淋油 把洋蔥炒到金黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金黃色？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炒完洋蔥之後 把土豆 胡蘿蔔 還有肉也炒一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 加入水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮一會以後 把蓋子拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把咖喱塊融進去就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 這個是佐料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力和？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變的超級好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯有點焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米飯真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱做的也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一點巧克力味都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有就不是佐料了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱隨便吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要添一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要加那麼多蛋黃醬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣還算少了 登山的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 隨便放哪裏都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 日向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 吃完也不收拾一個人在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵也進來嘛 很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 好了 大家排隊等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別人家的浴室讓人安靜不下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能伸展手腳的浴室真是好久沒泡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這浴室可真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服 舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:07:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 爸爸別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉 習慣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然覺得挺寬敞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4個人進來還是挺擠的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 再往那邊一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山間小屋的話 有時還會更擠的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了季節擠爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是坐滿了人的電車一樣擠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣還能睡得著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很累 所以睡得都很香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來製作荷蘭醬 要用很多黃油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著就很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次也做做看 火腿蛋吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來玩接龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用山的名字好像會很難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那從我開始 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個不算 那個 高尾山…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 恐山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不對 基拉威厄山 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}日本接龍如果最後一個音是n 則遊戲結束 不管是什麼山最後音一定是n
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜也深了 戀愛話題時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛話題？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有4個女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從葵開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在喜歡的人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米田君怎麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小學時代的話題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日向又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 楓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對夢馬君有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點橢圓臉 軟乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜幕降臨的那個山口 制動滑降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人會來嗎 帶著花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾卑斯的戀曲 心跳急速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟悉的登山家 溫柔的你呀溫柔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點日向 我絕不會棄你於不顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 我已經吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放棄 還差一點就要登頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們倆一起變得受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 你已經醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會讓人回憶起來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候 我們倆看見的朝陽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從富士山看的話 可能會更好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起住在帳篷裏真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我想去真正的山上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未完待續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
